[
  {
    "startTime": 0.2,
    "endTime": 3.7750000000000004,
    "text": "Now, I thought I'd share some of my favorite #WhyIQuit stories from you guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.9,
    "endTime": 6.6,
    "text": "This first one's from @SoupyMcSoupFace."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.976,
    "endTime": 17.278,
    "text": "He says, \"My boss refused to correct my name badge which said 'Brain' instead of 'Brian.' He said, 'You're Brain now, so deal with it.'\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.18,
    "endTime": 20.4,
    "text": "Right. Okay, Brain?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.5,
    "endTime": 22.689,
    "text": "Nope. Now I'm Soupy McSoupface."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.0,
    "endTime": 24.2,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.224,
    "endTime": 26.4,
    "text": "I'll show...I'll show him. I'll show him, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.3,
    "endTime": 31.5,
    "text": "\"You call me Brain, man?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.264,
    "endTime": 33.3,
    "text": "\"You can't call me Brain at all, man.\" \"Call me Soupy McSoupface.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.134,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "This one is from @toshoonly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.37,
    "endTime": 39.73,
    "text": "Toshoonly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.706,
    "endTime": 40.800000000000004,
    "text": "\"To\" like t-o."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.0,
    "endTime": 42.542,
    "text": "Like \"too shoon\"?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.542,
    "endTime": 43.2,
    "text": "Toshoon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.6,
    "endTime": 45.378,
    "text": "It's been too shoon. Too shoon. Too soon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.646,
    "endTime": 53.6,
    "text": "Toshoonly. She says, \"My boss made me give him piggyback rides after we mopped the floors every night so there would be fewer footprints.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.621,
    "endTime": 56.989000000000004,
    "text": "What?!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.989,
    "endTime": 58.23,
    "text": "Giddy-up! Giddy-up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.3,
    "endTime": 59.839999999999996,
    "text": "Let's go! Come on! Come on, Brain!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.5,
    "endTime": 63.83,
    "text": "What in the world? \"Come on, Brain!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.83,
    "endTime": 67.16499999999999,
    "text": "\"Don't be slippin' on that wet floor! Piso mojado!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.439,
    "endTime": 76.5,
    "text": "This one's from @bren_nancarrow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.809,
    "endTime": 83.877,
    "text": "She says, \"I babysat this kid who kept pointing at me and saying, 'You're next.'  After the fourth time, I gave my two weeks notice.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.419,
    "endTime": 87.3,
